title: Friday Morning Conversation With Jo Dee Messina + Bobby's Mailbag: Amy Called Out By Her Neighbor + Lunchbox Spills The Tea On Eddie
itunes:title: Friday Morning Conversation With Jo Dee Messina + Bobby's Mailbag: Amy Called Out By Her Neighbor + Lunchbox Spills The Tea On Eddie
description:
Jo Dee Messina stops by the studio for the 'Friday Morning Conversation'. Bobby opens up the mailbag and reads an email from one of Amy's neighbors about her being rude. Plus, Lunchbox spills the tea and calls out Eddie for stealing from the glass room.
